attachments.title: Blow-up metal technology • Materia
attachments.text: Talking about ‘blowing up metal objects’ often brings explosions to mind. But a technique developed over the last decade is rather more subtle, and looks set to make a mark in the manufacturing industry. Called FiDU, the technique involves welding thin metal plates together at their edges and then inflating them to create any number …
